snippet.title: Shining Princess Lapisphilia - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Store: https://saikeystudios.com/product/shining-princess-lapisphilia/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=post
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3253560/Shining_Princess_Lapisphilia/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=post

Lapisphilia, the Heroine of Justice, has thwarted the Gestarks one too many times! In a final bid for victory, they have created a dungeon as their last-ditch attempt to finally bring her to her knees! Fight through enemies and traps to escape and get back on surface!
